ai-mil3.4.9:1.2_0: “Reverend Sir, may all those who are gaining Nibbāna in Nibbāna?”
ai-mil3.4.9:1.3_0: “Great king, it is not possible to completely understand extinguishment; and one who practices it to completely understand extinguishment; and one who practices it should be developed by directly knowing this.”
ai-mil3.4.9:3.1_0: the ninth enquiry, the ninth (wholesome) gained Emancipation.
